El Sisi-witnesses today "Gulf shield "exercise in Saudi Arabia President Abdel Fattah El Sisi will attend on Monday 16/4/2018 the conclusion of the Joint Gulf Shield 1 drill Saudi Arabia's Eastern Region, Presidential Spokesman Ambassador Bassam Rady said on Sunday 15/4/2018. The Joint Gulf Shield 1 is taking place in the Eastern Region with participation of military forces from 24 countries as well as the Saudi forces.